xyz.fsgik.common.net.http

接口 FsHttpResponse


  • public interface FsHttpResponse
    Http response info, including status, headers and body.

    If the body of response is not null, that means the connection may not have been released yet, call InputStream.close() to release the connection. See getBody().

    • 方法概要

@Nullable java.io.InputStream getBody()
